high_descs: Turn and walk to the sinks on the right.
Open the cabinet door on the left side under the sink on the right, pick up a bottle, close the door.
Move to the counter between the two sinks.
Place the bottle down on the counter between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: To move a bottle from the cabinet to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and take one step, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet that is to the right of the pink bar of soap, below the sink and take out the bottle that is inside.
Turn left and take one step, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the bottle down on the counter to the right of the pink bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Move the bottle the counter top.

high_descs: Turn around completely and walk up to the bathroom counter.
Take out the lotion bottle that is in the left-hand cabinet under the right-hand sink.
Move over to the left a bit.
Place the lotion bottle down on the bathroom counter, to the right of the bar soap.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle of lotion to the bathroom counter.
